Genomic PCR of the four enlarged lymph nodes amplified the BLV env gene fragment in the first and second rounds of PCR (Fig. 2
). The same templates digested with restriction enzymes were subjected to iPCR, and in total, 29 clones were sequenced. All four tumor DNA samples digested with EcoRI and PstI contained the BLV provirus integrated into position 25,702,287 of chromosome 15. BssHII digestion did not give any positive signals. The integrated site was a non-transcriptional unit (Fig. 3
).
